title: Short Stories - Old and New - Pulsate
description:
[img]http://ebookjunkie.com/sites/default/files/styles/ebook_large/public/ebook_images/short-stories-old-new.jpg?itok=O78ASTtn[/img]

This book contains a wonderful collection of short stories you will love. There are a total of twelve stories. Here is a list of just a few of them:

Esther
The History of Ali Baba and the Forty Robbers
Rip Van Winkle
A Christmas Carol
This book is a must read for the young adult, or anyone who loves classic short stories.
